{
  "stem": "214.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "With wearing those high, black boots.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And, you know, he looks really like a real Ukrainian.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And there she comes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And there am I.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And that inn is full of Germans.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Because this was all the soldiers, all the officers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And there, you know, we sit down.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And she's serving us a dinner.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I am Fraulein Anna.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And you have plenty of those, you know, men around you.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Well, I went to-- I rented a little room.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And my friend thought that maybe I could remain there, you know, for the duration of the war.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But then, I didn't like it there at all, especially because I was surrounded by Germans.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And he wasn't my husband.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I didn't even know what happened to them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And about two or three days later, I decided I'm going back, I'm going back to Miedzyrzec, and I did.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And at strange coincidence, I come to-- I'm coming to Cracow again, and I have to wait again for the train.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And there, again, I'm surrounded by those Poles in the train, you know, who speak only about-- you know, one good thing about the fact that the Jews will be eliminated, what Hitler is doing for them.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And then, when we get up off the train-- must have been about 11 o'clock in the morning.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And this man asked me, do you have-- do you want to rest up for a few hours.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "He knows this lady here who is renting out rooms.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And would I go with him?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I don't see why I shouldn't.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean what else would I do?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we go up there, and he introduces me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, you know, and he-- he takes a room, and I take a room.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
